# bendd.me — Global Rules

See [AGENTS.md](../../AGENTS.md) for the full canonical reference and [docs/](../../docs/) for details.

## Critical Rules (Non-Negotiable)

1. **Tailwind `bd-` prefix**: ALL utility classes require `bd-` prefix
   - `bd-flex bd-gap-2 bd-text-foreground` (correct)
   - `flex gap-2 text-foreground` (wrong — will not work)
   - Variants: `hover:bd-bg-primary dark:bd-text-foreground md:bd-grid-cols-2`

2. **Package manager**: `pnpm` ONLY — `npm install` / `yarn add` cause lockfile conflicts

3. **Import alias**: `@/` ONLY — no relative imports (`../`)
   - `import { cn } from '@/lib/utils'` (correct)
   - `import { cn } from '../../lib/utils'` (wrong)

4. **Barrel exports**: Import domain components via `index.ts` only
   - `import { SoundSwitcher } from '@/components/sound'` (correct)
   - `import { SoundSwitcher } from '@/components/sound/ui/sound-switcher'` (wrong)

5. **Commits**: Conventional Commits + Korean messages
   - `feat(article): 블로그 글 검색 기능 추가` (correct)

## Content System

- `content/` → blog articles → `/article/[slug]` (use `createMDXProcessor()`)
- `craft/` → experimental → `/craft/[slug]` (use `createCraftMDXProcessor()`)
- Frontmatter limits: title <= 38 chars, summary <= 40 chars, description <= 150 chars

## Component Structure

```
src/components/{domain}/
├── index.ts    # Public API (barrel export — only import from here)
├── ui/         # React components
├── model/      # Hooks (use-*.ts), stores (*-store.ts)
├── types/      # Type definitions (.d.ts)
├── consts/     # Constants
└── lib/        # Utilities
```

## Key Patterns

- MDXProcessor uses immutable chaining with lazy evaluation
- Zustand stores use `persist` middleware with `bd-` prefixed storage keys
- Theme changes must sync with giscus via `postMessage` (see `useThemeManager`)
- Client-only components need `dynamic(() => import(...), { ssr: false })`
- CSS variables use HSL format: `hsl(var(--name))`

